Diamond::

She turned on the thrusters and tried to lift off.  She had to 
activate the auxillery drive to get off the ground. These bots where 
heavier than she thought.  She got the pod off the ground and hit the 
after burners and sped off towards the base. 

She turned to Killfest. "Comfy?"


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::Killfest/Greven/EndBringer::
> 
> Greven enters the pod, cramming himself into the back, Killfest 
> sitting down in the co-pilots seat, moving it back as far as he 
can. 
> The shuttle shakes slightly as EndBringer climbs on, adjusting his 
> electric tentacles to magnetically attatch to the shuttles.
> 
> "Let's go," Killfest says, uncomfortable with his knees almost up 
to 
> his chest. This shuttle was obvioustly not made for overgrown 
> terrorists.
